The official Python port of rocicorp/fractional-indexing (the Figma /
David-Greenspan fractional-indexing scheme). Vendored verbatim
(byte-faithful, attribution header prepended) inside `livespec_runtime`,
which has no vendoring machinery and is itself copied source-only into
every consumer's `_vendor/` tree, so the single ported file rides along
automatically. Exposed to livespec call sites only through the
keyword-only wrapper `livespec_runtime.work_items.rank`.

CC0 1.0 is a public-domain dedication: attribution is courteous, not
required. The full dedication text accompanies the upstream repository
